[ COUGHS, SNIFFLES ]

33:27.005 --> 33:29.800
SEE?

33:29.800 --> 33:31.593
AND EVERYTHING TASTES BAD.

33:31.593 --> 33:34.137
AND THIS FEVER'S,

33:31.593 --> 33:34.137
LIKE, BURNING ME UP.

33:34.137 --> 33:35.931
DO YOU HAVE A FEVER, MS. COWAN?

33:35.931 --> 33:39.225
A STUFFY NOSE? A RASH?

33:35.931 --> 33:39.225
