33:46.859 --> 33:50.278
YOURSELF, LADY.

33:52.197 --> 33:53.532
AH-CHOO!

33:53.532 --> 33:55.408
MS. COWAN,

33:53.532 --> 33:55.408
YOU DON'T THINK THAT --

33:55.408 --> 33:58.787
