34:00.664 --> 34:02.165
UGH!

34:04.793 --> 34:06.169
THIS IS CAROLINE'S FAVORITE.

34:06.169 --> 34:08.338
WHEN SHE DRINKS IT,

34:06.169 --> 34:08.338
IT'LL TASTE LIKE DUST.

34:08.338 --> 34:10.799
WHY? WHAT'S IN IT?

34:10.799 --> 34:13.092
FOOD COLORING AND DUST.

34:14.553 --> 34:16.095
TAKE THIS SHIRT. TAKE IT.

34:16.095 --> 34:18.473
MR. HALLIWARD IS ARRIVING

34:16.095 --> 34:18.473
FROM THE AIRPORT RIGHT NOW.

34:18.473 --> 34:19.850
GO.

34:19.850 --> 34:22.811
ALL RIGHT, JUST A LITTLE --

34:19.850 --> 34:22.811
LITTLE POWDER.

34:22.811 --> 34:25.981
IT'S FINE. JUST A LITTLE POWDER.

34:22.811 --> 34:25.981
IT'S OKAY.

34:27.357 --> 34:29.442
IT'S OKAY.

34:29.442 --> 34:31.361
