-HI. GOOD TO SEE YOU.

34:36.366 --> 34:38.076
-HEY, MARTIN.

34:38.076 --> 34:39.494
-FEEL BETTER, OKAY?

34:38.076 --> 34:39.494
-THANKS.

34:39.494 --> 34:41.371
MARTIN. [ LAUGHS ]

34:41.371 --> 34:44.082
YOU LOOK A HELL OF A LOT BETTER

34:41.371 --> 34:44.082
THAN THE LAST TIME I SAW YOU.

34:44.082 --> 34:45.834
THE DOC THINKS I'LL MAKE IT.

34:45.834 --> 34:48.003
[ LAUGHS ]

34:45.834 --> 34:48.003
I JUST WANTED TO THANK YOU.

34:48.003 --> 34:51.297
I HEARD WHAT YOU SAID TO BRYAN,

34:48.003 --> 34:51.297
AND AS MUCH AS I'D LIKE TO SEE

34:51.297 --> 34:53.341
THAT BOY GET

34:51.297 --> 34:53.341
WHAT'S COMING TO HIM,

34:53.341 --> 34:55.594
I AM AWFUL SORRY

34:53.341 --> 34:55.594
YOU LOST YOUR JOB.

34:55.594 --> 34:57.136
OH, DON'T WORRY ABOUT THAT.

34:57.136 --> 34:59.431
LIKE I SAID,

34:57.136 --> 34:59.431
I'M JUST PASSING THROUGH.

34:59.431 --> 35:01.516
NO WAY TO RUN A BUSINESS,

34:59.431 --> 35:01.516
IF YOU ASK ME.

35:01.516 --> 35:03.142
NO, IT'S NOT.

35:03.142 --> 35:04.561
YOU KNOW, I-I WISH I STILL HAD

35:04.561 --> 35:06.229
THAT OLD HARDWARE STORE

35:04.561 --> 35:06.229
KICKING AROUND.

35:06.229 --> 35:09.190
YOU'D BE A GOOD MAN

35:06.229 --> 35:09.190
TO HAVE HANDY.

35:16.990 --> 35:18.324
HEY, ENJOYING THE BARBECUE?

35:18.324 --> 35:20.243
AND YOU FOUND YOURSELF

35:18.324 --> 35:20.243
SOMETHING?

35:20.243 --> 35:21.995
THAT'S -- THAT'S GOOD.

35:21.995 --> 35:23.538
You've reached

35:21.995 --> 35:23.538
the mayor's office.

35:23.538 --> 35:25.206
Please leave a message

35:23.538 --> 35:25.206
after the beep.

35:25.206 --> 35:27.918
MR. MAYOR,

35:25.206 --> 35:27.918
THIS IS MY THIRD VOICEMAIL,

35:27.918 --> 35:31.212
SO I'M BEGINNING TO THINK

35:27.918 --> 35:31.212
THAT YOU'RE AVOIDING ME.

35:31.212 --> 35:33.381
YOU REMEMBER THAT RATHER

35:31.212 --> 35:33.381
LARGE DONATION WE MADE

35:33.381 --> 35:34.925
TO YOUR RE-ELECTION CAMPAIGN?

35:34.925 --> 35:36.551
WELL, YOU KNOW SOMETHING

35:34.925 --> 35:36.551
ABOUT THIS PIECE OF PROPERTY

35:36.551 --> 35:38.136
THAT YOU'RE NOT TELLING ME,

35:36.551 --> 35:38.136
DON'T Y--

35:38.136 --> 35:40.138
CAROLINE. [ LAUGHS ]

35:40.138 --> 35:41.598
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

35:41.598 --> 35:44.142
HELLO, MR. HALLIWARD.

35:41.598 --> 35:44.142
WELCOME TO APPLE SPRINGS.

35:44.142 --> 35:45.602
WE ARE SO HAPPY TO HAVE YOU.

35:45.602 --> 35:47.353
IT'S GOOD TO SEE YOU AGAIN,

35:45.602 --> 35:47.353
CAROLINE.

35:47.353 --> 35:48.730
WONDERFUL TURNOUT.

35:48.730 --> 35:50.065
THANK YOU.

35:50.065 --> 35:53.819
ARE YOU OKAY?

35:50.065 --> 35:53.819
YOU LOOK A LITTLE FLUSHED.

35:53.819 --> 35:55.988
JUST, YOU KNOW, TOO MUCH SUN.

35:55.988 --> 35:57.405
HOW ABOUT A TOUR?

35:57.405 --> 35:59.741
I'D LOVE TO SEE

35:57.405 --> 35:59.741
WHAT YOU'VE DONE WITH THE PLACE.

35:59.741 --> 36:00.909
MM-HMM.

36:00.909 --> 36:03.286
[ LAUGHS ] OKAY. FOLLOW ME.

36:03.286 --> 36:05.538
SO, THIS IS OUR BREAK ROOM,

36:05.538 --> 36:07.791
WHICH WE MADE

36:05.538 --> 36:07.791
A LITTLE SMALLER IN THIS ONE,

36:07.791 --> 36:10.669
BUT JUST SAVE A LITTLE MONEY,

36:07.791 --> 36:10.669
AND I THINK IT REALLY WORKS.

36:10.669 --> 36:13.130
ARE YOU SURE YOU'RE

36:10.669 --> 36:13.130
FEELING ALL RIGHT, CAROLINE?

36:13.130 --> 36:14.506
YOU SEEM A LITTLE OFF.

36:14.506 --> 36:16.675
NO. I-I'M FINE.

36:16.675 --> 36:18.677
LIFE ON THE ROAD --

36:16.675 --> 36:18.677
THAT CAN'T BE EASY.

36:18.677 --> 36:20.386
ALL RIGHT, PEOPLE,

36:18.677 --> 36:20.386
PLACE YOUR BETS.

36:20.386 --> 36:21.763
DON'T THINK WE HAVEN'T NOTICED.

36:21.763 --> 36:23.431
100 BUCKS GETS YOU IN.

36:23.431 --> 36:25.142
THE SUCCESS OF THIS STORE

36:23.431 --> 36:25.142
IS JUST THE CHERRY ON TOP.

36:25.142 --> 36:27.602
I'M IN. FIVE MINUTES.

36:27.602 --> 36:29.270
-SHE'LL GO SEVEN.

36:27.602 --> 36:29.270
-I SAY THREE MINUTES.

36:29.270 --> 36:31.481
-I'M UNDER TWO.

36:29.270 --> 36:31.481
-ALL RIGHT, UNDER TWO.

36:31.481 --> 36:33.066
YOU GOT THREE, FIVE --

36:31.481 --> 36:33.066
FIVE, SEVEN.

36:33.066 --> 36:34.233
MM-HMM.

36:34.233 --> 36:36.153
I'M VERY IMPRESSED

36:34.233 --> 36:36.153
WITH THIS STORE,

36:36.153 --> 36:39.322
AND I'D LIKE YOU TO JOIN US

36:36.153 --> 36:39.322
AT CORPORATE HEADQUARTERS.

36:41.240 --> 36:42.659
OH.

36:42.659 --> 36:44.577
OH, THANK YOU, SIR.

36:42.659 --> 36:44.577
YOU WON'T REGRET THIS.

36:44.577 --> 36:46.913
I'LL BE ON A PLANE

36:44.577 --> 36:46.913
FIRST THING TOMORROW MORNING.

36:46.913 --> 36:48.206
AND -- AND I'M READY TO GO.

36:48.206 --> 36:50.000
NOT SO FAST.

36:50.000 --> 36:53.419
YOU'VE MADE AN ENORMOUS IMPACT

36:50.000 --> 36:53.419
WITH THIS STORE IN JUST A WEEK.

36:53.419 --> 36:57.090
I'D LIKE TO SEE HOW THIS

36:53.419 --> 36:57.090
NEW BUSINESS STRATEGY OF YOURS

36:57.090 --> 36:59.009
WORKS OUT IN THE LONG RUN.

37:01.094 --> 37:02.303
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

37:02.303 --> 37:04.430
OH, STICK AROUND TOWN

37:02.303 --> 37:04.430
A LITTLE LONGER,

37:04.430 --> 37:06.474
MAYBE SIX MONTHS.

37:06.474 --> 37:09.477
NO.

37:06.474 --> 37:09.477
PLEASE DON'T MAKE ME, SIR.

37:09.477 --> 37:10.937
I CAN'T.

37:10.937 --> 37:13.523
THIS STORE IS NOT SAFE.

37:13.523 --> 37:14.816
IT'S POISONED.

37:14.816 --> 37:16.943
OOH. THAT WAS QUICK.

37:16.943 --> 37:19.112
OH, YEAH! COME TO MAMA!

37:20.197 --> 37:22.365
ALL RIGHT, SO, WHAT DO YOU SAY,

37:20.197 --> 37:22.365
UH, WE BROADCAST?

37:22.365 --> 37:24.117
I SAY LET'S DO IT.

37:24.117 --> 37:27.079
[ BEEPING ]

37:27.079 --> 37:29.330
POISON? WHAT POISON?

37:29.330 --> 37:31.166
THE GROUND UNDERNEATH US

37:29.330 --> 37:31.166
IS TOXIC.

37:31.166 --> 37:33.543
SHE TRIED TO WARN ME,

37:31.166 --> 37:33.543
BUT I WOULDN'T LISTEN.

37:33.543 --> 37:35.962
-WHO IS SHE?

37:33.543 --> 37:35.962
-OH, GONE BECAUSE OF ME.

37:35.962 --> 37:38.715
I BURIED EVIDENCE BECAUSE

37:35.962 --> 37:38.715
I KNEW YOU'D WANT ME TO.

37:38.715 --> 37:41.300
MY GOD! WHAT KIND OF

37:38.715 --> 37:41.300
COMPANY LIABILITY ARE

37:38.715 --> 37:41.300
WE TALKING ABOUT HERE?

37:41.300 --> 37:43.011
WELL, WHAT DOES IT MATTER NOW?

37:43.011 --> 37:45.222
WE BOTH KNOW THIS COMPANY

37:43.011 --> 37:45.222
IS ROTTEN FROM THE INSIDE OUT,

37:45.222 --> 37:46.264
AND WE KNOW HOW THIS WORKS.

37:46.264 --> 37:47.849
WE TRIED TO BRIBE THIS CITY

37:47.849 --> 37:49.768
JUST TO GET THIS BUILDING

37:47.849 --> 37:49.768
IN THE FIRST PLACE,

37:49.768 --> 37:51.477
BUT THIS TIME, WE REALLY GOT

37:49.768 --> 37:51.477
WHAT WE PAID FOR, DIDN'T WE?

37:51.477 --> 37:53.563
AND THESE POOR SLOBS

37:51.477 --> 37:53.563
SELLING OUR SWEATSHOP CRAP

37:53.563 --> 37:56.066
AREN'T EVEN GONNA HAVE HEALTH

37:53.563 --> 37:56.066
