37:56.066 --> 37:57.734
AND THEY'RE GONNA GET SICK.

37:57.734 --> 37:59.527
CAROLINE,

37:57.734 --> 37:59.527
GET AHOLD OF YOURSELF.

37:59.527 --> 38:01.738
DON'T LOOK AT ME

37:59.527 --> 38:01.738
LIKE THAT, SIR.

38:01.738 --> 38:03.865
IF YOU THINK I'M GONNA DIE

38:01.738 --> 38:03.865
FOR THIS COMPANY,

38:03.865 --> 38:06.576
YOU CAN THINK AGAIN.

38:06.576 --> 38:08.620
STOP!

38:12.874 --> 38:15.710
GET ME CORPORATE ON THE PHONE!

38:20.840 --> 38:22.341
[ SIGHS ]

38:27.222 --> 38:29.141
[ GASPS ]

38:42.070 --> 38:44.697
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

38:44.697 --> 38:46.741
WE'LL BE IN TOUCH.

38:46.741 --> 38:50.036
SIR, WE HAVE A DAMAGE-CONTROL

38:46.741 --> 38:50.036
PRESS CONFERENCE IN 20 MINUTES.

38:50.036 --> 38:52.914
CANCEL IT.

38:50.036 --> 38:52.914
THIS STORE IS A LOST CAUSE.

38:58.253 --> 38:59.504
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

