THE LOCAL SHOPS HAVE REOPENED.

39:03.591 --> 39:05.718
EVERYBODY THAT GOT LAID OFF

39:03.591 --> 39:05.718
HAS A JOB.

39:05.718 --> 39:07.137
WHAT ABOUT THE BUILDING?

39:07.137 --> 39:09.222
I HEARD AN ANONYMOUS DONOR

39:07.137 --> 39:09.222
PUT IN A BID FOR IT.

39:09.222 --> 39:12.309
HE SAID HE'S GONNA TURN

39:09.222 --> 39:12.309
IT INTO A THEATER FOR

39:09.222 --> 39:12.309
THE LOCAL HIGH SCHOOL.

39:12.309 --> 39:15.436
THE ARTS ARE VASTLY

39:12.309 --> 39:15.436
UNDERFUNDED IN THIS

39:12.309 --> 39:15.436
COUNTRY, DON'T YOU THINK?

39:15.436 --> 39:18.064
YOU SLY OLD DOG.

39:18.064 --> 39:20.150
OH, BABE, THE CANDY SHOPPE'S

39:18.064 --> 39:20.150
OPEN. YOU IN?

39:20.150 --> 39:23.278
-SOUNDS GOOD.

39:20.150 --> 39:23.278
-ALL RIGHT.

39:29.742 --> 39:32.245
SECOND WIFE.

39:29.742 --> 39:32.245
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

