-HEY.

39:33.663 --> 39:35.207
-HOW YOU DOING?

39:33.663 --> 39:35.207
-I'M GOOD.

39:35.207 --> 39:36.457
HOW'S HE WORKING OUT?

39:36.457 --> 39:39.002
OH, YOU KNOW,

39:36.457 --> 39:39.002
HE'S FITTING RIGHT IN.

39:39.002 --> 39:41.338
SO, THANK YOU FOR

39:39.002 --> 39:41.338
EVERYTHING THAT YOU DID.

39:41.338 --> 39:43.882
IT'S STARTING TO FEEL LIKE HOME

39:41.338 --> 39:43.882
AGAIN AROUND HERE.

39:43.882 --> 39:47.844
WOULD YOU, UH...

39:47.844 --> 39:50.722
WOULD YOU LIKE TO HAVE

39:47.844 --> 39:50.722
DINNER...WITH ME?

39:52.682 --> 39:54.600
-TONIGHT?

39:52.682 --> 39:54.600
-HOW'S SATURDAY?

39:54.600 --> 39:57.436
I GOT TO GO OUT OF TOWN

39:54.600 --> 39:57.436
FOR A COUPLE OF DAYS.

39:57.436 --> 40:00.439
I WOULD LOVE THAT.

40:00.439 --> 40:02.483
GOOD.

